name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hatsune Miku China Dress Live Wallpaper

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add a touch of elegance and charm to your browser with the Hatsune Miku China Dress Live Wallpaper.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension features the iconic virtual singer Hatsune Miku, dressed in a beautiful traditional Chinese dress, with stunning details and dynamic effects. The graceful movements of Hatsune Miku bring a refreshing and artistic vibe to your new tab.

Features:
🌸 Elegant live wallpaper of Hatsune Miku in a traditional China dress.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display to keep you on track.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Let the beauty and style of Hatsune Miku elevate your browsing experience every time you open a new tab.
